1.Open 'edit environment variables for your account'
2.Creat/Update Varaible = 'Path', Value should be as   C:\Users\[your user name]\Anaconda3\Scripts;C:\Users\[your user name]\Anaconda3;C:\Users\[your user name]\Anaconda3\Library\bin
3. Open Command Prompt and Check Versions
4. After 7th step type conda install anaconda-navigator in cmd then press y
Then should be all set

